        "modelVersion": "ansys-cfx-hemolysis-2026-q1-build-7-rc2",
        "description": "Release candidate build immediately preceding the production release. Patch delta relative to released build: single correction to near-wall shear-stress interpolation in the k-omega SST turbulence closure. Patch was deemed non-impactful for rotating-machine hemolysis QoIs by the solver development team based on a single impeller benchmark."
      },
      "comparisonMetric": "Normalized Index of Hemolysis (NIH) vs. clinical threshold",
      "comparisonOutcome": "Pass — all five operating points satisfy NIH < 0.01 g/100 L at 95th percentile of Monte Carlo distribution"
