      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against in-vitro hemolysis measurements using modified power-law model. E_rms = 12.4% across five operating points. Experimental uncertainty (±9%) overlaps simulation 95th-percentile interval at four of five points. One outlier at 6 L/min / 3000 RPM not fully explained."
