      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same device geometry, fluid, and operating envelope as the COU.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used in both validation and COU prediction. Blood analog fluid (glycerin-water) used in experiments; porcine blood used in COU. Species-specific rheological differences introduce unquantified extrapolation uncertainty."
    },
    {
