      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed over seven input parameters (viscosity, density, inlet velocity profile shape, rotational speed tolerance, hemolysis model coefficients C and alpha). Blood viscosity distribution based on literature meta-analysis; individual patient variability not captured. Three inputs (surface roughness, impeller tip clearance, outlet pressure) treated as deterministic due to lack of characterization data."
    },
