      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from published FDA benchmark study (Hariharan et al.). Number of replicate pump units tested in the source study is not reported with sufficient detail to confirm three independent articles. Inter-sample variability not separable from run-to-run variability in available data. Factor flagged as not-assessed pending data access."
