    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the evidence package on the basis that all seven assessed credibility factors show achieved levels within one gradation of required levels, and that the Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates NIH below the absolute clinical threshold with 95% confidence. The team further accepted the validation results generated under solver configuration ansys-cfx-hemolysis-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 as applicable to the released build ansys-cfx-hemolysis-2026-q1-build-7, characterizing the intervening patch as a non-impactful single-module correction based on internal benchmark testing. No re-execution of validation runs under the released build was required.",
